      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; use of published FDA round-robin data is sufficient.",
      "rationale": "Validation leverages the multi-laboratory FDA round-robin dataset (n=6 laboratories). Formal test-sample adequacy assessment is not required at MRL 2."
    },
